Greetings! 

  Sorry for my poor English...I have improved the texture for female. At least i think that it seem better. Used photoshop to draw the basic pattern and create a Chinese dragon on her back. Unfortunately, I had no time to make lace. But i will improve it next version or another mods. This one includes the main meshes and textures, and the PDB file too. If you don\'t like the style, you can try to adjust yourself.

Have fun! 

================================================================
P.s. 
Copy the \'Data\' folder into your Skyrim directory.
